title: Grade (Band) - Discography
description:
Albums

    * And Such Is Progress (May 1997 Toybox Records)
    * Under the Radar (October 12, 1999)
    * The Embarrassing Beginning (November 21, 2000)
    * Headfirst Straight to Hell (August 21, 2001)

EPs

    * Separate The Magnets (1997 Second Nature Recordings)
    * Triumph and Tragedy (August 3, 1999)

Singles

    * Gathering Darkness (Punk Goes Acoustic)

According to wikipedia, there was an early EP called S/T 7", but I don't know anything about it. Also, all the songs on Triumph and Tragedy are included on The Embarrassing Beginning, although they might be slightly different versions.
